{"id": "1485672193634467960", "channel_id": "1485672193634467960", "type": 0, "author_id": "1151402965001838673", "author_name": "the_wolfice.", "author_bot": false, "content": "是被莫絲這個角色吸引來的！本來對這種卡牌遊戲不是很感興趣，但是朋友很推薦來玩玩看這個遊戲，而且莫絲也超可愛的☺️，人物的立繪風格也很戳我，所以就開始玩啦\n\n不過目前對這個遊戲的各方面都不是很了解，像抽卡規劃和角色配隊之類的，聽朋友的建議來國際服請教大佬，目前如果想玩莫絲隊可以怎麼組？ 有特別需要抽的隊友嘛？", "timestamp": "2026-03-23T16:10:53.417000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1485672194234257438", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-03-23-23-50-39-704_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 204145}, {"id": "1485672194913865779", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-03-23-23-50-53-538_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 193063}, {"id": "1485672197962989680", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-03-23-23-52-00-913_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 188872}, {"id": "1485672198336286974", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-03-23-23-52-12-469_com.sialiagames.z1.gp.twnew.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 166651}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1485676798984585286", "channel_id": "1485672193634467960", "type": 0, "author_id": "357866427421687818", "author_name": "passerbycat", "author_bot": false, "content": "便宜一點的配置大概就是(但可能需要2-3啟才會比較好玩)\n莫絲 拉蒙娜 珊 希萊斯特\n\n莫絲帶界域 拉蒙娜帶銀鑰\n珊帶死抗 希萊看缺啥帶啥\n\n想要高一點貴一點的\n可以找克珀珊特 誕妄墨菲 彌利亞姆這些角色入隊\n常見的有\n船長 二四 莫絲 融朵\n船長 莫絲 魔術師 墨菲/醫生", "timestamp": "2026-03-23T16:29:11.418000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-03-23T16:29:50.095000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
